87
00:04:17,199 --> 00:04:18,279
I don't believe it.

88
00:04:19,959 --> 00:04:20,680
Baby,

89
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:21,600
I will

90
00:04:21,839 --> 00:04:22,839
