91
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:26,720
Director Qian.

92
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:29,199
Who let you in?

93
00:04:29,199 --> 00:04:30,160
Where's Qiqi?

94
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:31,720
I'm sorry, Director Qian.

95
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:32,879
Well, Qiqi

96
00:04:32,879 --> 00:04:35,040
